text: Wynncraft is a Minecraft server, that homes a Minecraft massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) game. Wynncraft was made mostly by Jumla, Salted, and Grian, and it was released in April of 2013. One server owner, Salted, said on Twitter, that over 2.9 million players had joined the server at one point, as of March 2021. == Reception == Wynncraft has been highly perceived, for having complete gameplay, all on Minecraft. Some reviewers praised the game for it's use of Minecrafts vanilla tools, to create a full MMO game. According to Guinness World Records, in July of 2017, it was the biggest MMORPG game built on Minecraft. == References == == Other websites == *Official website *Official wiki Category:Minecraft Category:Massively multiplayer online role-playing games
